er_writer, train_loss_path.open(\nscripts/final_training.py:409:                current_step, losses = train_to_step(\nscripts/final_training.py:452:                    \"full_parameter_training\": True,\nscripts/final_training.py:472:        \"train_loss_summary\": summarize_losses(all_losses),\nscripts/final_training.py:473:        \"train_loss_path\": str(train_loss_path),\nscripts/final_training.py:543:        \"primary_condition\": \"structured_pt_seed_a\",\nscripts/final_training.py:637:            \"- The final training data reuses the immutable pilot split artifacts and cycles them to the target-token budget.\",\nscripts/final_training.py:643:            \"- Repeated small split examples can overfit; report train/eval split hashes and treat this as a narrow final trajectory.\",\nscripts/final_training.py:658:        \"phase\": \"02_final_training\",\nscripts/final_training.py:689:## {timestamp} - TinyStories-8M final behavioral trajectories complete\nscripts/final_training.py:691:Decision: proceed to the LLC campaign with behavior outputs and checkpoint-selection rules frozen. No final LLC traces were inspected or optimized during final behavioral training.\nscripts/final_training.py:695:Conditions: structured Portuguese seed A, token-shuffled Portuguese, matched English, and structured Portuguese seed B completed in the predeclared priority order using full-parameter AdamW continued pretraining on `roneneldan/TinyStories-8M`.\nscripts/final_training.py:709:                \"02_final_training\",\nscripts/final_training.py:727:    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser(description=\"TinyStories-8M final behavioral trajectories\")\nscripts/final_training.py:746:    tokenizer = AutoTokenizer.from_pretrained(cfg.model, local_files_only=cfg.local_files_only)\nscripts/final_training.py:749:    model_probe = AutoModelForCausalLM.from_pretrained(cfg.model, local_files_only=cfg.local_files_only)\nscripts/final_training.py:761:        \"run_kind\": \"tinystories_8m_final_be